                "category": "summary",
                "text": "NVIDIA has released a software update for NVIDIA\u00ae Triton Inference Server. <br><div>To protect your system, clone or update this software to Triton Server r26.02 or later from the NVIDIA <a href=\"https://github.com/triton-inference-server/server\">Triton Inference Server </a>GitHub repo.</div>",
